              essential details, including the event schedule, venue
              information, dress code, RSVP options, and travel arrangements. We
              look forward to sharing this beautiful day with you and creating
              unforgettable memories together!
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="card-footer">
            <p>Meer informatie over:</p>
            <ul>
              <li><a href="">Programma</a></li>
              <li><a href="#aanmelden">Aanmelden</a></li>
              <li><a href="#thema">Thema</a></li>
              <li><a href="#locatie">Locatie</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card-image">
          <Image src={Riley} alt="" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="aanmelden">
      <div class="text">
        <div class="block-title">
          <h2 class="oranje">We horen graag of je erbij bent!</h2>
          <p class="text-subtle paars">Vier met ons!</p>
        </div>
        <SigninForm />
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="thema" class="backdrop">
      <div class="text backdrop-text">
